before a job is launched (or in some cases in the middle of a running job).

But it would be possible to write a custom component that was hardcoded 
via its source code. Since you mention MySQL DB credentials, and no 
component using such credentials is part of standard Heritrix, it&#39;s 
possible your custom component has this limitation.

